Title: Testing the Addition of an Anti-cancer Drug, Entinostat, to the Usual Chemotherapy and Immunotherapy Treatment (Atezolizumab, Carboplatin and Etoposide) for Previously Untreated Aggressive Lung Cancer That Has Spread
Conditions: Extensive Stage Lung Small Cell Carcinoma, Malignant Solid Neoplasm, Metastatic Malignant Neoplasm in the Brain
Phase: PHASE1
Status: COMPLETED
Primary outcomes: Number of Participants With Dose Limiting Toxicities; Number of Participants Experiencing Grade 3 and 4 Adverse Events; Number of Participants Who Received 3 or More Cycles of the Combination of Entinostat, Atezolizumab, Carboplatin, and Etoposide